SUMMARY:Von Decarlo LIVE at Punch Line Irving
DESCRIPTION:This post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you. \nOfficial Tickets\nResale Tickets \nVon Decarlo LIVE at Punch Line Irving\nDon’t miss Von Decarlo as she brings her bold\, unapologetic stand-up comedy to Punch Line Irving on Wednesday\, July 1\, 2026. Known for her fearless humor and magnetic stage presence\, Von Decarlo delivers a show packed with laughs\, real talk\, and unforgettable moments. \nEvent Details\nDate: Wednesday\, July 1\, 2026\nTime: 7:30 PM CDT\nVenue: Punch Line Irving\nAddress: 310 W Las Colinas Blvd.\, Suite 130\, Irving\, TX 75039\nAge Requirement: 18+ (valid government-issued photo ID required)\nMinimum: 2-beverage minimum per person \nAbout Von Decarlo\nVon Decarlo is a rising stand-up comedian and social media sensation known for her candid\, hilarious takes on relationships\, life\, and pop culture. With a massive following on TikTok and Instagram\, she has built a devoted fanbase who love her no-filter approach to comedy. Her live shows are an extension of her authentic\, laugh-out-loud personality. \nWhat to Expect\n\nBold\, unapologetic stand-up comedy\nHilarious takes on relationships and everyday life\nIntimate comedy club atmosphere at Punch Line Irving\nFull bar and beverage service during the show\n18+ event — bring valid government-issued photo ID\nLimited seating — tickets selling fast\n\nVenue Information\nPunch Line Irving is the DFW area’s newest premier comedy club\, located at 310 W Las Colinas Blvd.\, Suite 130 in Irving\, Texas. The venue offers a full bar\, cashless payment\, and an intimate setting perfect for live stand-up comedy. \nTicket Information\nTickets start at $27.65 and are on sale now. Only 84 tickets remaining — don’t wait! All sales are final. A 2-beverage minimum per person applies. Doors open one hour before show time. \nOfficial Tickets\nResale Tickets \nThis post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you. \nAll sales are final. Show times subject to change. Valid photo ID required for entry. 18+ event.
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/von-decarlo-live-at-punch-line-irving/
LOCATION:Punch Line Irving\, 310 W Las Colinas Blvd.\, Suite 130\, Irving\, TX\, 75039\, United States Of America
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/a/380/40bb836f-46b6-4515-9fbc-21f5a430d380_TABLET_LANDSCAPE_LARGE_16_9.jpg
GEO:32.8734455;-96.9445654
