SUMMARY:Mario Adrion LIVE at San Jose Improv
DESCRIPTION:Official TicketsResale Tickets \nAbout the Performer\nMario Adrion is a stand-up comedian from a small town in Germany who has taken the internet — and the world — by storm. With over 3.5 million followers across social media platforms\, Mario built his fanbase through refreshingly honest and self-deprecating comedy that resonates with audiences everywhere. \nHis comedy is uniquely vulnerable\, playing with the struggles and stereotypes of being a retired male model and a European navigating life in the United States. Think fish-out-of-water humor with a sharp\, charming twist — and a German accent that makes everything funnier. \nOver the past few years\, Mario has toured his wildly popular “The German EFiciency Tour” around the world\, selling out shows across the US\, UK\, Europe\, and the Middle East. He filmed his debut hour-long special in January 2026 and is now embarking on an even bigger international tour\, “The Superior Comedy Tour\,” performing in clubs and theaters across the globe. Based out of Los Angeles\, Mario Adrion is one of the hottest rising comics in the game right now. \nEvent Details\n\nDate: Wednesday\, July 1\, 2026\nShow Time: 7:30 PM PDT (Doors open at 6:00 PM)\nVenue: San Jose Improv\, 62 S Second St\, San Jose\, CA 95113\nAge Restriction: 21+ Event — Valid ID required at the door\nContent: Stand-up comedy — clean\, relatable\, and hilarious\n\nAbout the Venue\nThe San Jose Improv is one of the Bay Area’s premier stand-up comedy clubs\, located in the heart of downtown San Jose at 62 S Second St. Part of the nationally renowned Improv comedy club chain\, the San Jose Improv has hosted some of the biggest names in comedy and continues to be the go-to destination for world-class stand-up in Silicon Valley. \nThe intimate club setting creates an electric atmosphere where every seat feels close to the stage. The venue features a full-service bar and dining menu\, with a mandatory two-item minimum purchase per guest in the showroom. Seating is general admission and first-come\, first-served (with the exception of groups and premium booths)\, so arriving early is recommended to secure the best spots. \nThe San Jose Improv is easily accessible in downtown San Jose\, with multiple parking garages and public transit options nearby. The venue’s cozy\, club-style layout ensures an up-close and personal comedy experience that larger theaters simply can’t match. \nWhat to Expect\nExpect a night of sharp\, self-aware comedy that blends European sensibility with American pop culture observations. Mario Adrion’s show is a solo stand-up performance — no openers\, just Mario and his signature storytelling style that has captivated millions online. \nHis material draws heavily from his own life: the absurdity of being a former model\, the culture shock of moving from Germany to the US\, and the universal awkwardness of modern life. Fans of his social media content will recognize his style immediately — but live\, it hits on a completely different level. \nThis is a 21+ event\, so bring your ID. The two-item minimum at the Improv means you’ll be sipping something while you laugh — which honestly just makes the whole experience better. No phones\, no photography\, no recording during the show. Just pure\, unfiltered comedy. \nTicket Information\nPrice Range: $25 – $90 (plus fees) \n\nGA Ticket: $25 (+ fees)\nVIP Ticket: $40 (+ fees) — preferred seating\n\n\n\nOfficial TicketsResale Tickets \nThis post contains affiliate links. We may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/mario-adrion-live-at-san-jose-improv/
LOCATION:San Jose Improv\, 62 S Second St\, San Jose\, California\, 95113\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://i.ticketweb.com/i/00/13/35/04/23_Edp.jpg?v=5
GEO:37.3356413;-121.8883224
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=San Jose Improv 62 S Second St San Jose California 95113 United States;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=62 S Second St:geo:-121.8883224,37.3356413
END:VEVENT
