SUMMARY:Wingman Wednesdays Miami’s Social Comedy Show
DESCRIPTION:Blackbird Ordinary. Meet new people. Laugh at hilarious dating stories. Join the conversation. Ladies drink free during showtime 9-10:30 PM.\n\n\nA fun night out where people happen to meet. \nWingman Wednesdays is Miami’s social comedy show where dating\, relationships\, and modern romance become the night’s entertainment. Hosted by Miami’s Best Comedian Manny Garavito and Miami’s Best Master of Ceremonies Luke Prince\, the show stirs up live comedy\, tasteful crowd interaction\, audience stories\, terrible dating advice\, red flags\, green flags\, first dates on the spot\, and the hilarious realities of navigating Miami’s social scene. \nWhether you’re single\, taken\, in the alphabet\, somewhere in between\, or just here to watch the tea spill\, you’ll be part of a night filled with laughs\, unexpected moments\, and real conversations. Audience participation is encouraged but never required\, making it just as fun to watch as it is to jump in. \nBring your friends\, your situationships\, your worst dating stories\, but most importantly your sense of humor. \nLadies drink free during showtime from 9:00 PM to 10:30 PM. \nComedy. Cocktails. Questionable decisions. \nTopics include but are not limited to: \nBrickell finance bros \nYacht season \nSugar daddy retirement plans \nInstagram followers \n“What do you do?” stress tests \nPenthouse with air matresses \nDating apps \nGym culture \nPlastic surgery \nSpiritual girls \nHow to Ghost 101 \nToxic Green Flags \n…And enough unsolicited dating advice to keep everyone single a little longer. \nCome watch. Come participate. Or just sit back and enjoy the turbulence. \nTicket Options \nGeneral Admission (FREE: frist come\, first serve)First come\, first served. Whatever seats are not purchased will be available to anyone who arrives early. Once they’re gone\, they’re gone. \n$25 Guaranteed Seating + Wingmen for HireSkip the rush and secure your seats in advance. Plus\, you’ll be guaranteed an opportunity to join Manny and Luke on stage for live crowd interaction\, dating advice\, matchmaking attempts\, relationship advice\, or whatever romantic turbulence the evening encounters. Limited spots available. \n$50 VIP Flight Crew Experience (Guaranteed Seating\, Wingmen for Hire\, VIP Bottle Afterparty Access AND Merch)Everything included: guaranteed seating\, Wingman for hire\, access to our bottle section for the afterparty with Manny and Luke\, plus exclusive Miami Comedy merch to take home. VERY Limited spots.
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/wingman-wednesdays-miamis-social-comedy-show-3/
LOCATION:Blackbird Ordinary\, Southwest 1st Avenue 729\, Miami\, FL\, 33130\, United States
CATEGORIES:Events,Showcase,Stand-Up Comedy
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://comedycalendar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Wingman-Wednesday-Banner-EB-l6o0Gy.png
GEO:25.7666715;-80.1951345
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Blackbird Ordinary Southwest 1st Avenue 729 Miami FL 33130 United States;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=Southwest 1st Avenue 729:geo:-80.1951345,25.7666715
END:VEVENT
