DESCRIPTION:This post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you. \nOfficial Tickets\nResale Tickets \nMorgan Jay: The Goofy Guy Tour LIVE at Premier Theater at Foxwoods Resort Casino\nRising comedy star Morgan Jay brings his wildly popular Goofy Guy Tour to the Premier Theater at Foxwoods Resort Casino in Mashantucket\, CT on July 2\, 2026. Known for his infectious energy\, relatable storytelling\, and hilarious crowd work\, Morgan Jay delivers a comedy experience unlike any other. \nEvent Details\nDate: Thursday\, July 2\, 2026\nTime: 7:00 PM (Doors open 6:00 PM)\nVenue: Premier Theater at Foxwoods Resort Casino\nAddress: 39 Norwich Westerly Road\, Mashantucket\, CT 06339\nAge Requirement: 16 & Over\nTicket Prices: Starting at $34 \nAbout Morgan Jay\nMorgan Jay is a fast-rising comedian who has taken the comedy world by storm with his viral videos\, sold-out tours\, and Netflix appearances. His debut feature film premiered at SXSW 2025 in the Narrative Spotlight section\, cementing his status as one of comedy’s brightest new stars. His Goofy Guy Tour has been selling out venues across the country. \nWhat to Expect\n\nHigh-energy stand-up comedy performance\nHilarious crowd interaction and improvisation\nRelatable storytelling and observational humor\n16+ event at a world-class casino resort venue\nOne of comedy’s hottest rising stars live on stage\nUnforgettable night of laughs at Foxwoods\n\nVenue Information\nThe Premier Theater at Foxwoods Resort Casino is a state-of-the-art entertainment venue located at 39 Norwich Westerly Road in Mashantucket\, CT. The theater offers excellent sightlines\, premium seating\, and all the amenities of the world-famous Foxwoods Resort Casino complex. \nTicket Information\nTickets start at $34 and are available now. This is a 16+ event. All ticket sales are final and non-refundable. Purchase official tickets through Ticketmaster or find resale tickets on VividSeats. \nOfficial Tickets\nResale Tickets \nThis post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you.\nAll sales are final. Show times subject to change. Valid photo ID may be required for entry.
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/morgan-jay-the-goofy-guy-tour-live-at-premier-theater-at-foxwoods-resort-casino/
