SUMMARY:Tommy Davidson LIVE at Brea Improv
DESCRIPTION:This post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you. \nOfficial Tickets (Ticketmaster) \nResale Tickets (VividSeats) \nTommy Davidson LIVE at Brea Improv\nComedy legend Tommy Davidson brings his exceptional stand-up comedy to the Brea Improv for a multi-night run in July 2026. \nBest known as one of the stars of the hit TV show In Living Color\, Tommy Davidson is a versatile entertainer whose range spans stand-up\, acting\, and music. \nEvent Details\nDate: Thursday\, July 2\, 2026\nTime: 8:00 PM PDT (Doors open at 6:30 PM)\nVenue: Brea Improv\nAddress: 180 S Brea Blvd\, Brea\, CA 92821\nAge Requirement: 21+\nSeating: General Admission\, first-come first-served\nNote: Two-item minimum purchase required \nAbout Tommy Davidson\nTommy Davidson is best known as one of the original cast members of In Living Color\, where his impressions of Sammy Davis Jr. and Michael Jackson became iconic. He has starred in Disney’s The Proud Family\, appeared in films like Ace Ventura II and Bamboozled\, and continues to headline major comedy venues across the country. \nWhat to Expect\n\nHigh-energy stand-up from an In Living Color legend\nHilarious impressions and character work\nIntimate club setting at the Brea Improv\nVIP seating options available\n21+ show with full bar and two-item minimum\n\nVenue Information\nBrea Improv is located at 180 S Brea Blvd in Brea\, CA. Part of the legendary Improv comedy club chain in Orange County\, CA. \nTicket Information\nTickets start at $25 (plus fees). VIP from $40. GA Booths from $75. VIP Premium Booths from $90. \nOfficial Tickets (Ticketmaster) \nResale Tickets (VividSeats) \nThis post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you. \nAll sales are final. Show times subject to change. Valid photo ID may be required for entry.
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/tommy-davidson-live-at-brea-improv/
LOCATION:Brea Improv\, 180 South Brea Blvd\, Brea\, CA\, 92821\, United States
