SUMMARY:Beth Stelling LIVE at Jimmy Kimmel's Comedy Club
DESCRIPTION:Official TicketsResale Tickets \nAbout the Performer\nBeth Stelling is one of the most celebrated stand-up comedians working today\, known for her razor-sharp wit\, deeply personal storytelling\, and fearless honesty on stage. \nHer comedy blends confessional vulnerability with biting humor\, tackling topics like relationships\, identity\, and the absurdities of everyday life with a refreshing authenticity. \nStelling has appeared on Netflix\, Comedy Central\, and Late Night with Seth Meyers\, and her acclaimed special Girl Daddy earned widespread critical praise for its emotional depth and comedic precision. \nEvent Details\n\nDate: Friday\, July 3\, 2026\nShow Time: 7:30 PM (doors open earlier)\nVenue: Jimmy Kimmel’s Comedy Club\, 3545 S Las Vegas Blvd\, Las Vegas\, NV 89109\nAge Restriction: 18+ Event\nTicket Prices: From $63\n\nAbout the Venue\nJimmy Kimmel’s Comedy Club is one of the premier comedy destinations on the Las Vegas Strip\, located on the iconic LINQ Promenade at 3545 S Las Vegas Blvd. \nThe intimate venue seats approximately 300 guests and features a state-of-the-art sound system\, excellent sightlines from every seat\, and a full bar service throughout the show. \nThe club’s cozy atmosphere creates an up-close-and-personal comedy experience unlike the large arena shows Vegas is known for. Parking is available at the LINQ Hotel parking garage\, and the venue is easily accessible via the Las Vegas Monorail. \nThe LINQ Promenade itself offers a variety of dining and entertainment options before and after the show\, making it a perfect evening destination. \nWhat to Expect\nBeth Stelling delivers a headline solo stand-up performance packed with her signature blend of personal storytelling and sharp observational comedy. \nExpect an intimate\, high-energy show where Stelling connects directly with the audience through her candid\, relatable humor. Her sets are known for building emotional momentum — drawing laughs while also leaving audiences genuinely moved. \nThis is a rare opportunity to see one of comedy’s most talked-about voices in an intimate Las Vegas club setting. Arrive early to secure the best seats and enjoy a drink before the show. \nTicket Information\nTickets start from $63 and are available through official and resale channels. \nOfficial TicketsResale Tickets \nThis post contains affiliate links. We may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/beth-stelling-live-at-jimmys-kimmels-comedy-club/
LOCATION:Jimmy Kimmel’s Comedy Club\, 3545 S Las Vegas Blvd\, Las Vegas\, NV\, 89109\, USA
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://comedycalendar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/383ac4be-5cc9-498b-83e1-5ecc560cbf09_CUSTOM-viuPP0.jpg
GEO:36.11759;-115.168698
