SUMMARY:DeRay Davis LIVE at The Theater at MGM National Harbor
DESCRIPTION:This post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you. \nOfficial Tickets\nResale Tickets \nDeRay Davis LIVE at The Theater at MGM National Harbor\nDeRay Davis\, one of comedy’s most electrifying performers\, brings his high-energy stand-up show to The Theater at MGM National Harbor in National Harbor\, Maryland for a special July 4th weekend performance. Known for his explosive delivery and hilarious storytelling\, DeRay is set to deliver a night of non-stop laughs. \nEvent Details\nDate: Friday\, July 3\, 2026\nTime: 8:00 PM\nVenue: The Theater at MGM National Harbor\nAddress: 101 MGM National Ave\, National Harbor\, MD 20745\nAge Requirement: 18+ (valid photo ID required) \nAbout DeRay Davis\nDeRay Davis is a Chicago-born stand-up comedian and actor best known for his roles in films like 21 Jump Street and Barbershop\, as well as his appearances on Wild ‘N Out. With a style that blends sharp observational humor with raw street comedy\, DeRay has built a massive following through his Netflix specials and sold-out live shows across the country. \nWhat to Expect\n\nHigh-energy stand-up comedy from one of the game’s best\nHilarious stories drawn from real life and pop culture\nA perfect July 4th weekend night out in the DC/Maryland area\nWorld-class venue with excellent sightlines and sound\nAn unforgettable evening of laughs at MGM National Harbor\n\nVenue Information\nThe Theater at MGM National Harbor is a premier entertainment venue located just minutes from Washington\, DC\, offering state-of-the-art acoustics\, comfortable seating\, and a full casino resort experience. The venue hosts top-tier comedy\, music\, and entertainment acts year-round. \nTicket Information\nTickets are available now through Ticketmaster (official) and VividSeats (resale). Secure your seats early as this show is expected to sell out for the holiday weekend. \nOfficial Tickets\nResale Tickets \nThis post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you.\nAll sales are final. Show times subject to change. Valid photo ID may be required for entry.
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/deray-davis-live-at-the-theater-at-mgm-national-harbor/
LOCATION:The Theater at MGM National Harbor\, 101 MGM National Ave\, National Harbor\, MD\, 20745\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/a/332/b7e2b245-267c-402a-a78f-c50f46a63332_TABLET_LANDSCAPE_LARGE_16_9.jpg
