SUMMARY:"Weird Al" Yankovic: Bigger & Weirder 2026 Tour LIVE at Acrisure Amphitheater
DESCRIPTION:This post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you. \nOfficial Tickets\nResale Tickets \n“Weird Al” Yankovic: Bigger & Weirder 2026 Tour LIVE at Acrisure Amphitheater\nThe legendary “Weird Al” Yankovic is bringing his highly anticipated  to the Acrisure Amphitheater in Grand Rapids\, Michigan on July 3\, 2026. With special guest Puddles Pity Party\, this Fourth of July weekend show promises to be an unforgettable night of comedy\, music\, and pure entertainment. \nEvent Details\nDate: Friday\, July 3\, 2026\nTime: 8:00 PM (Doors open earlier)\nVenue: Acrisure Amphitheater\nAddress: 201 Market Ave SW\, Grand Rapids\, MI 49503\nSpecial Guest: Puddles Pity Party\nAge Requirement: All Ages \nAbout “Weird Al” Yankovic\n“Weird Al” Yankovic is the best-selling comedy recording artist of all time\, known for his hilarious parodies of pop hits and original comedy songs spanning over four decades. With 5 Grammy Awards\, 15 studio albums\, and a career that has made him a cultural icon\, Weird Al continues to delight audiences of all ages with his unique blend of music and comedy. His 2022 biopic WEIRD: The Al Yankovic Story introduced him to a whole new generation of fans. \nWhat to Expect\n\nHilarious parodies of your favorite pop songs performed live\nElaborate costume changes and theatrical production value\nA high-energy\, family-friendly comedy and music extravaganza\nSpecial guest performance by the beloved Puddles Pity Party\nPerfect Fourth of July weekend entertainment for the whole family\nDecades of hits from one of comedy’s greatest performers\n\nVenue Information\nAcrisure Amphitheater is Grand Rapids’ premier outdoor amphitheater\, located at 201 Market Ave SW in the heart of downtown Grand Rapids\, Michigan. The venue offers excellent sightlines\, great acoustics\, and a fantastic outdoor concert experience along the Grand River. \nTicket Information\nTickets start from approximately $54 and are available through Ticketmaster (official tickets) and VividSeats (resale tickets). Secure your seats early as this Fourth of July weekend show is expected to sell out! \nOfficial Tickets\nResale Tickets \nThis post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you. \nAll sales are final. Show times subject to change. Valid photo ID may be required for entry.
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/weird-al-yankovic-bigger-weirder-tour-live-at-acrisure-amphitheater/
LOCATION:Acrisure Amphitheater\, 201 Market Ave SW\, Grand Rapids\, Michigan\, 49503\, United States
