SUMMARY:"Weird Al" Yankovic LIVE at The Colosseum at Caesars Windsor
DESCRIPTION:This post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you. \nOfficial Tickets\nResale Tickets \n“Weird Al” Yankovic LIVE at The Colosseum at Caesars Windsor\nThe legendary “Weird Al” Yankovic is bringing his Bigger & Weirder 2026 Tour to Windsor\, Ontario for an unforgettable all-ages show at The Colosseum at Caesars Windsor on Saturday\, July 4\, 2026. Known for his hilarious parody songs and outrageous live performances\, Weird Al delivers a spectacular concert experience packed with comedy\, music\, and non-stop entertainment. \nEvent Details\nDate: Saturday\, July 4\, 2026\nTime: 8:00 PM (Doors open 7:00 PM)\nVenue: The Colosseum at Caesars Windsor\nAddress: 377 Riverside Drive East\, Windsor\, Ontario\, Canada N9A 7H7\nAge Requirement: All Ages Welcome\nParking: Complimentary parking in attached six-level parking garage \nAbout “Weird Al” Yankovic\n \nWhat to Expect\n\nA high-energy\, full-production concert featuring Weird Al’s greatest parody hits\nMultiple costume changes and theatrical set pieces throughout the show\nClassic parodies including “Eat It\,” “Amish Paradise\,” “White & Nerdy\,” and more\nSpecial guest Puddles Pity Party joining the tour\nAn all-ages family-friendly comedy concert experience\nUnforgettable moments of laughter and musical brilliance\n\nVenue Information\nThe Colosseum at Caesars Windsor is one of Canada’s premier entertainment venues\, located at 377 Riverside Drive East in Windsor\, Ontario\, just across the border from Detroit. The venue features world-class amenities\, complimentary parking\, and easy access from both Canada and the United States. \nTicket Information\nTickets for “Weird Al” Yankovic: Bigger & Weirder 2026 Tour start from $118. There is an overall 4-ticket limit per order. Tickets are available through Ticketmaster (official) and VividSeats (resale). \nOfficial Tickets\nResale Tickets \nThis post contains affiliate links. We earn a commission if you purchase tickets through our links at no extra cost to you. \nAll sales are final. Show times subject to change. Valid photo ID may be required for entry.
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/weird-al-yankovic-live-at-the-colosseum-at-caesars-windsor/
LOCATION:The Colosseum at Caesars Windsor\, 377 Riverside Dr E\, Windsor\, ON\, N9A 7H7\, Canada
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://comedycalendar.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/ce609b68-dd49-4ebc-a034-6b52a6a67e23_TABLET_LANDSCAPE_LARGE_16_9-xcO57t.jpg
GEO:42.3200781;-83.0336202
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=The Colosseum at Caesars Windsor 377 Riverside Dr E Windsor ON N9A 7H7 Canada;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=377 Riverside Dr E:geo:-83.0336202,42.3200781
END:VEVENT
