SUMMARY:Comedy Cellar Las Vegas (Late)
DESCRIPTION:This post contains affiliate links. We may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. \n\nOfficial Tickets\n\nResale Tickets\n\nComedy Cellar Las Vegas brings one of the most legendary names in stand-up comedy to the heart of Las Vegas. Located inside the Rio Hotel & Casino\, this intimate comedy club is the West Coast home of New York City’s world-famous Comedy Cellar\, the venue that helped launch the careers of comedy icons including Dave Chappelle\, Chris Rock\, Jon Stewart\, Ray Romano\, Amy Schumer\, Aziz Ansari\, and countless others. \nUnlike traditional comedy shows featuring a single headliner\, Comedy Cellar presents a carefully curated lineup of professional comedians every night. Audiences can expect multiple performers during each show\, featuring a mix of nationally touring headliners\, television favorites\, Comedy Central veterans\, Netflix performers\, and rising stars from around the world. \nNo two shows are exactly alike\, making every visit a unique experience. Surprise drop-in appearances from major comedians performing elsewhere in Las Vegas have become part of the club’s reputation\, giving audiences the chance to see comedy superstars in an intimate setting. \nEvent Details\nVenue: Comedy Cellar Las Vegas at Rio Hotel & Casino\nLocation: 3700 W Flamingo Rd\, Las Vegas\, NV 89103\nShow Schedule: Nightly performances throughout the year\nAge Requirement: Recommended for audiences 18+ due to mature comedy content \nAbout the Venue\nOpened in 2018\, Comedy Cellar Las Vegas was designed to recreate the atmosphere and energy of the original Greenwich Village club that has become one of the most respected comedy venues in the world. The 300-seat showroom offers excellent sightlines and an intimate setting that allows audiences to experience stand-up comedy exactly as it was meant to be seen: up close and personal. \nThe venue combines the excitement of a Las Vegas night out with the authentic feel of a classic New York comedy club. Guests can enjoy a comfortable showroom environment while watching some of the best comedians working today perform in a setting that encourages spontaneity\, crowd interaction\, and unforgettable moments. \nConveniently located inside the Rio Hotel & Casino just minutes from the Las Vegas Strip\, the venue offers easy access for both tourists and local comedy fans. \nWhat to Expect\nExpect a fast-paced evening featuring multiple comedians performing throughout the show. The Comedy Cellar is known for showcasing a wide variety of comedic styles\, from observational humor and storytelling to sharp social commentary\, crowd work\, and cutting-edge stand-up. \nWhether you’re discovering a future comedy star or watching a seasoned veteran perfect their craft\, every show delivers the authentic comedy club experience that has made the Comedy Cellar one of the most respected brands in stand-up comedy. \nFor comedy fans visiting Las Vegas\, Comedy Cellar is widely considered one of the best places in the city to experience live stand-up comedy any night of the week.
URL:https://comedycalendar.com/event/comedy-cellar-las-vegas-late/2026-07-04/
